      <title>白宫称拜登将减刑另外 2,500 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/biden-will-commute-another-2-500-sentences-white-house-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周五在一份声明中表示，总统乔·拜登将减轻近 2,500 名非暴力毒品犯罪分子的刑期，这些犯罪分子的刑期比现行标准规定的刑期要长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/biden-will-commute-another-2-500-sentences-white-house-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本现在预计将无法实现 2025 年基本平衡目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/japan-now-expects-to-miss-its-2025-primary-balance-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的基本收支平衡势必再次无法实现其在2026年3月之前实现预算平衡的长期目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/japan-now-expects-to-miss-its-2025-primary-balance-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:57:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利突袭反腐败办公室 指控其涉嫌欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/hungarian-prosecutors-raid-anti-graft-office-over-alleged-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利反腐败机构本身也陷入了贪污调查，此前检察官突击搜查了该机构的办公室，指控其滥用资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/hungarian-prosecutors-raid-anti-graft-office-over-alleged-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国财政部长称政府垮台影响经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/french-finance-chief-says-government-collapse-dented-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国新任财政部长埃里克·隆巴德 (Eric Lombard) 表示，上个月法国政府倒台导致经济产出下降了 0.3 个百分点，并且国家失去了修复预算所急需的税收收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/french-finance-chief-says-government-collapse-dented-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:06:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长亚当斯计划与特朗普举行就职前会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/new-york-mayor-adams-plans-pre-inauguration-meeting-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯将于周五与唐纳德·特朗普会面，讨论纽约人的优先事项，这是陷入困境的民主党领袖与长期称纽约市为家乡的共和党当选总统之间合作的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/new-york-mayor-adams-plans-pre-inauguration-meeting-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙停火后，胡塞武装表示暂停对红海船只的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/houthis-signal-pause-on-red-sea-ship-attacks-after-gaza-truce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列与哈马斯达成停火协议后，驻扎在也门的胡塞武装表示将暂停长达数月的对商船的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/houthis-signal-pause-on-red-sea-ship-attacks-after-gaza-truce</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾马科斯称现在不是弹劾副总统杜特尔特的时候</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/philippines-marcos-says-now-isn-t-time-to-impeach-vp-duterte</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯表示，弹劾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特的企图是不合时宜的，因为议员们将在 5 月份的中期选举前非常忙碌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/philippines-marcos-says-now-isn-t-time-to-impeach-vp-duterte</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:18:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班称欧盟应终止对俄罗斯的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/eu-should-move-to-end-sanctions-against-russia-orban-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班表示，欧盟应该终止对俄罗斯的制裁，因为唐纳德·特朗普政府准备从下周开始开启“新时代”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/eu-should-move-to-end-sanctions-against-russia-orban-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国调查小组寻求新的逮捕令以延长尹某的逮捕期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/south-korean-president-yoon-remains-in-detention-for-time-being</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，韩国总统尹锡烈因发布不合时宜的戒严令而遭弹劾，韩国调查人员随即申请签发新的逮捕令，以延长对他的拘留时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/south-korean-president-yoon-remains-in-detention-for-time-being</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 03:03:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特顺利通过参议院质询，为确认候选人铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/bessent-says-us-barreling-toward-crisis-if-tax-cuts-not-extended</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长提名人斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 有望在周四的确认听证会上获得确认，此次听证会没有特朗普政府一些候选人所面临的戏剧性场面，问题主要集中在联邦预算和贸易关税等政策问题上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/bessent-says-us-barreling-toward-crisis-if-tax-cuts-not-extended</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 16:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
